Subject: [PATCH 1/2] ggml-cuda: add pool1d op and fix binbcast indexing

This patch is intended to be applied on top of whisper.cpp commit
`9c807c8056f8b3da89ede02015cef942f77de01b`.

- Adds CUDA support for GGML_OP_POOL_1D (needed by pyannote segmentation).
- Fixes binbcast indexing types and access pattern.

